						               													<description>What happens when you throw a pack of crazy Monster Trucks, a limited supply of Nitro, and a bunch of irresponsible drivers on a track? Monster Truck Madness! In this competitive, demo-derby racer there is only one rule - win! Will you choose to out-race, outmaneuver, or simply demolish your opponents on the way to the finish line? Jam packed with high horse-power action, questionable tactics and head-to-head collision, MTM is a diesel-fueled dash to the finish line!  Throw in innovative Braking and Damage systems, 10 mean Monsters with unique abilities and play-styles, and the ability to Upgrade your Truck with a slew of outrageous Augments and you have a recipe for all out Vehicular Warfare!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Monster Truck Madness, players will take the role of Monster Truck drivers in a competitive, demo-derby style race!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After choosing their unique Truck, players will role the Speed die to advance around one of the unique Race Tracks, making use of Braking to avoid hazards and burning Nitro for speed. Along the way, players will Challenge other drivers they encounter, with the loser being damaged and Wrecked (losing a turn).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner of a Challenge will also receive a Scrap Token, which can be turned in for one of 9 unique Upgrades to benefit their truck at the Pit-Stop.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To determine the winner, points are scored at the end of the final lap based on finishing position, bonus points for demolishing players, and certain cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
